{"tid":1641084,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"四種黃店 Four Shades of Yellow","createTime":"2019-10-09T08:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T08:45:57.000Z","uid":190579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5d356a76263fec1cc521281a99581d36e325a1d0","tid":1641084,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:40:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 舊黃</span></strong></span><br />\n一早已經開始黃，參與過八五大罷既<br />\n呢種一定要用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>行動</strong></span>懲罰啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">接下來就係裝修盛行之後<span style=\"color: purple;\">離奇</span>變黃既店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 紅黑變黃</span></strong></span><br />\n二坡坊，優品360呢D，明顯啦<br />\n劈完人say 個sorry 就原諒？<br />\n一次已經足夠永不原諒<br />\n唔通的士佬出嚟嗌句光時你又原諒佢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔應該鼓勵，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">維持原判</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">頂多接受有條件投降，唔再犯就唔再裝修(反正都已經裝無可裝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">3. 藍變黃</span></span></strong><br />\n呢D又係牆頭草<br />\n個人認為亦都應該<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>維持原判</strong></span><br />\n第一，佢哋唔係真心黃，極之虛偽<br />\n第二，佢哋轉黃係為利益。自撚私，唔會對運動有實質貢獻。就算有，都只係由傻黃身上賺既錢攞少少出嚟。<br />\n第三，一日政府得勢，佢哋又會倒戈。<br />\n三姓家奴，養嚟做乜？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4. 中立變黃</span></span></strong><br />\n呢種黃先係可以唯一可以入<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>觀察名單</strong></span>既黃<br />\n可吸納可鼓勵<br />\n佢哋有好多嘢可以幫到抗爭既，如果係真心黃自然會識do<br />\n我亦都唔希望大家訂定準則叫佢哋做<br />\n就好似送紀念日禮物比男女朋友咁<br />\n重點係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">真心</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係交功課交戲"},{"pid":"bf90da0653fe29c4c3549dce460ec9205981da64","tid":1641084,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:40:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"25bea5d90df6fc63f587ab963c68082231ed64ca","tid":1641084,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eba499530aaa0c4879222af3453b85424d1a0bc","tid":1641084,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78adb9a233c3f8a2d93a2ba27954084857df091","tid":1641084,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">「Xinnie the Pooh」Challenge</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q3PNSB7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3PNSB7.png&h=70fa4b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4UBLW8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4UBLW8.png&h=10505b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"},{"pid":"13935ee6a9a72fbf3198d15de7538de5bfb5bffb","tid":1641084,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EGVxFacUYAAAuP0?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEGVxFacUYAAAuP0%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D900x900&h=29081802&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cba6198dd22c840321e49b79a0315f019a06c3d5","tid":1641084,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}